{"id":8281,"date":"2024-11-12T11:49:12","date_gmt":"2024-11-12T04:49:12","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/hanoireview.vn\/?p=8281"},"modified":"2025-03-12T11:39:14","modified_gmt":"2025-03-12T04:39:14","slug":"hinh-anh-dep-ve-pho-co-ha-noi","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/hanoireview.vn\/hinh-anh-dep-ve-pho-co-ha-noi-8281.html","title":{"rendered":"BST Nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u0111\u1eb9p v\u1ec1 Ph\u1ed1 C\u1ed5 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i g\u1ee3i nh\u1edb k\u00fd \u1ee9c"},"content":{"rendered":"<p class=\"p1\"><strong>Ph\u1ed1 c\u1ed5 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t kh\u00f4ng gian \u0111\u1eadm ch\u1ea5t v\u0103n h\u00f3a v\u00e0 l\u1ecbch s\u1eed m\u00e0 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 n\u01a1i h\u1ed9i t\u1ee5 nh\u1eefng n\u00e9t \u0111\u1eb9p \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ea5t kinh k\u1ef3 x\u01b0a. Qua t\u1eebng g\u00f3c ph\u1ed1, t\u1eebng con ng\u00f5 nh\u1ecf h\u1eb9p, t\u1eebng ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 c\u1ed5 k\u00ednh, ph\u1ed1 c\u1ed5 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i ph\u00e1c h\u1ecda l\u00ean m\u1ed9t b\u1ee9c tranh s\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1ec1 n\u00e9t x\u01b0a c\u0169 nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn r\u1ed9n r\u00e0ng trong d\u00f2ng ch\u1ea3y hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i. <\/strong><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\">Nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh v\u1ec1 ph\u1ed1 c\u1ed5 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 l\u01b0u l\u1ea1i kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1eb9p c\u1ee7a n\u01a1i n\u00e0y, gi\u00fap ng\u01b0\u1eddi xem c\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o s\u1ef1 tinh t\u1ebf, c\u1ed5 k\u00ednh v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7y ch\u1ea5t th\u01a1 c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i.<\/p>\n<p class=\"p3\"><b>Con ph\u1ed1 c\u1ed5 k\u00ednh, \u0111\u1eadm ch\u1ea5t ho\u00e0i ni\u1ec7m<\/b><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\">Ph\u1ed1 c\u1ed5 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng con ph\u1ed1 nh\u1ecf h\u1eb9p m\u00e0 c\u00f2n mang \u0111\u1eadm d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n l\u1ecbch s\u1eed v\u00e0 v\u0103n h\u00f3a, l\u00e0 n\u01a1i ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta b\u1eaft g\u1eb7p nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 m\u00e1i ng\u00f3i r\u00eau phong, c\u1eeda g\u1ed7 \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea1c m\u00e0u th\u1eddi gian, v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng d\u00e3y nh\u00e0 san s\u00e1t nhau v\u1edbi ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac x\u01b0a c\u0169. Nh\u1eefng b\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh v\u1ec1 ph\u1ed1 c\u1ed5 lu\u00f4n ghi l\u1ea1i n\u00e9t \u0111\u1eb9p tr\u1ea7m m\u1eb7c c\u1ee7a con ph\u1ed1, n\u01a1i m\u00e0 t\u1eebng chi ti\u1ebft nh\u1ecf nh\u01b0 c\u1ed9t \u0111\u00e8n, b\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u1eddng hay nh\u1eefng bi\u1ec3n hi\u1ec7u c\u0169 k\u1ef9 \u0111\u1ec1u g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n l\u00e0m n\u00ean d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_8319\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8319\" style=\"width: 768px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-8319 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/hanoireview.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/hinh-anh-ve-pho-co-ha-noi-1731383172.jpg\" alt=\"h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh v\u1ec1 ph\u1ed1 c\u1ed5 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i\" width=\"768\" height=\"511\" srcset=\"https:\/\/hanoireview.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/hinh-anh-ve-pho-co-ha-noi-1731383172.jpg 768w, https:\/\/hanoireview.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/hinh-anh-ve-pho-co-ha-noi-1731383172-455x303.jpg 455w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-8319\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Nh\u00e0 c\u1ed5 M\u00e3 M\u00e2y \u2013 N\u00e9t \u0111\u1eb9p v\u0103n h\u00f3a c\u00f2n s\u00f3t l\u1ea1i cu\u1ed1i th\u1ebf k\u00fd 19<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<figure id=\"attachment_8324\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8324\" style=\"width: 768px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-8324 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/hanoireview.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/hinh-anh-ve-pho-co-ha-noi-1731384051.jpg\" alt=\"h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u0111\u1eb9p v\u1ec1 ph\u1ed1 c\u1ed5 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i\" width=\"768\" height=\"576\" srcset=\"https:\/\/hanoireview.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/hinh-anh-ve-pho-co-ha-noi-1731384051.jpg 768w, https:\/\/hanoireview.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/hinh-anh-ve-pho-co-ha-noi-1731384051-453x340.jpg 453w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-8324\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">\u0110\u1ec1n Ng\u1ecdc S\u01a1n &#8211; Bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng ngh\u00ecn n\u0103m v\u0103n hi\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<figure id=\"attachment_8343\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8343\" style=\"width: 768px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-8343 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/hanoireview.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/hinh-anh-ve-pho-co-ha-noi-1731385082.jpg\" alt=\"h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u0111\u1eb9p v\u1ec1 ph\u1ed1 c\u1ed5 h\u00e0 n\u1ed9i\" width=\"768\" height=\"512\" srcset=\"https:\/\/hanoireview.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/hinh-anh-ve-pho-co-ha-noi-1731385082.jpg 768w, https:\/\/hanoireview.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/hinh-anh-ve-pho-co-ha-noi-1731385082-455x303.jpg 455w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-8343\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">C\u1eeda \u00f4 Quan Ch\u01b0\u1edfng l\u00fac ho\u00e0ng h\u00f4n g\u1ee3i m\u1ed9t n\u00e9t ho\u00e0i c\u1ed5 tr\u1ea7m l\u1eafng<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p class=\"p3\"><b>Nh\u1ecbp s\u1ed1ng s\u00f4i \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 duy\u00ean d\u00e1ng gi\u1eefa l\u00f2ng Th\u1ee7 \u0110\u00f4<\/b><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\">Tr\u00e1i v\u1edbi v\u1ebb y\u00ean \u1ea3 c\u1ee7a bu\u1ed5i s\u1edbm mai, v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00e1c trong ng\u00e0y, ph\u1ed1 c\u1ed5 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i hi\u1ec7n l\u00ean \u0111\u1ea7y s\u00f4i \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1edbi d\u00f2ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi qua l\u1ea1i t\u1ea5p n\u1eadp, v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng h\u00e0ng qu\u00e1n bu\u00f4n b\u00e1n \u0111\u1ee7 lo\u1ea1i t\u1eeb hoa qu\u1ea3, h\u00e0ng \u0103n \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed3 th\u1ee7 c\u00f4ng m\u1ef9 ngh\u1ec7. C\u00e1c b\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh v\u1ec1 ph\u1ed1 c\u1ed5 trong kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc n\u00e0y th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n nh\u1ecbp s\u1ed1ng th\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u1eadt \u0111\u1ea7y s\u1ee9c s\u1ed1ng v\u00e0 tr\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7y n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a con ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u01a1i \u0111\u00e2y. S\u1eafc m\u00e0u r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng g\u00e1nh hoa, tr\u00e1i c\u00e2y, c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi ti\u1ebfng rao th\u00e2n thu\u1ed9c t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t b\u1ee9c tranh ch\u00e2n th\u1eadt v\u00e0 g\u1ea7n g\u0169i v\u1ec1 cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng \u1edf ph\u1ed1 c\u1ed5.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_8326\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8326\" style=\"width: 768px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-8326 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/hanoireview.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/hinh-anh-ve-pho-co-ha-noi-1731384114.jpg\" alt=\"h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u0111\u1eb9p v\u1ec1 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i\" width=\"768\" height=\"538\" srcset=\"https:\/\/hanoireview.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/hinh-anh-ve-pho-co-ha-noi-1731384114.jpg 768w, https:\/\/hanoireview.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/hinh-anh-ve-pho-co-ha-noi-1731384114-455x319.jpg 455w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-8326\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ph\u1ed1 bia T\u1ea1 Hi\u1ec7n s\u00f4i \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00eam<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p class=\"p3\"><b>Bu\u1ed5i s\u00e1ng y\u00ean b\u00ecnh v\u00e0 ph\u00fat l\u1eb7ng c\u1ee7a chi\u1ec1u t\u00e0<\/b><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\">Nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc b\u00ecnh minh v\u00e0 ho\u00e0ng h\u00f4n t\u1ea1i ph\u1ed1 c\u1ed5 lu\u00f4n mang \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c l\u00e3ng m\u1ea1n v\u00e0 thanh b\u00ecnh. \u00c1nh n\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ng\u00e0y nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng soi r\u1ecdi xu\u1ed1ng nh\u1eefng con ph\u1ed1 v\u1eafng ng\u01b0\u1eddi, l\u00e0m n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt m\u00e0u xanh c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng t\u00e1n c\u00e2y c\u1ed5 th\u1ee5 v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3n chi\u1ebfu nh\u1eefng m\u1ea3ng t\u01b0\u1eddng nhu\u1ed1m m\u00e0u th\u1eddi gian.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_8284\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8284\" style=\"width: 768px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-8284 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/hanoireview.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/hinh-anh-ve-pho-co-ha-noi-1731378206.jpg\" alt=\"h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u0111\u1eb9p v\u1ec1 ph\u1ed1 c\u1ed5 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i\" width=\"768\" height=\"512\" srcset=\"https:\/\/hanoireview.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/hinh-anh-ve-pho-co-ha-noi-1731378206.jpg 768w, https:\/\/hanoireview.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/hinh-anh-ve-pho-co-ha-noi-1731378206-455x303.jpg 455w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-8284\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">M\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i s\u00e1ng b\u00ecnh y\u00ean tr\u00ean ph\u1ed1 c\u1ed5 v\u1edbi tia n\u1eafng chi\u1ebfu qua h\u00e0ng c\u00e2y<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<figure id=\"attachment_8329\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8329\" style=\"width: 768px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-8329 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/hanoireview.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/hinh-anh-ve-pho-co-ha-noi-1731384267.jpg\" alt=\"h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u0111\u1eb9p v\u1ec1 ph\u1ed1 c\u1ed5 h\u00e0 n\u1ed9i\" width=\"768\" height=\"432\" srcset=\"https:\/\/hanoireview.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/hinh-anh-ve-pho-co-ha-noi-1731384267.jpg 768w, https:\/\/hanoireview.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/hinh-anh-ve-pho-co-ha-noi-1731384267-455x256.jpg 455w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-8329\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh m\u1ed9t g\u00e1nh h\u00e0ng hoa g\u1ee3i n\u00ean m\u1ed9t v\u1ebb \u0111\u1eb9p b\u00ecnh d\u1ecb gi\u1eefa th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p class=\"p1\">V\u00e0o l\u00fac chi\u1ec1u t\u00e0, ph\u1ed1 c\u1ed5 kho\u00e1c l\u00ean m\u00ecnh v\u1ebb tr\u1ea7m m\u1eb7c, nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 d\u1ea7n ch\u00ecm v\u00e0o b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1i, \u00e1nh \u0111\u00e8n l\u1ea5p l\u00f3 t\u1eeb c\u00e1c c\u1eeda h\u00e0ng t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t khung c\u1ea3nh b\u00ecnh y\u00ean v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7y ch\u1ea5t th\u01a1. H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh v\u1ec1 ph\u1ed1 c\u1ed5 v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y th\u01b0\u1eddng mang l\u1ea1i c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng, th\u01b0 th\u00e1i v\u00e0 c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n ho\u00e0i ni\u1ec7m cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi xem.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_8323\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8323\" style=\"width: 768px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-8323 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/hanoireview.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/hinh-anh-ve-pho-co-ha-noi-1731383914.jpg\" alt=\"h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u0111\u1eb9p v\u1ec1 ph\u1ed1 c\u1ed5 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i\" width=\"768\" height=\"512\" srcset=\"https:\/\/hanoireview.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/hinh-anh-ve-pho-co-ha-noi-1731383914.jpg 768w, https:\/\/hanoireview.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/hinh-anh-ve-pho-co-ha-noi-1731383914-455x303.jpg 455w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-8323\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">M\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i chi\u1ec1u y\u00ean \u1ea3 tr\u00ean ph\u1ed1 c\u1ed5 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p class=\"p3\"><b>Kh\u00f4ng gian v\u0103n ho\u00e1 \u0111\u1eadm \u0111\u00e0 b\u1ea3n s\u1eafc<\/b><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\">Ph\u1ed1 c\u1ed5 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i c\u00f2n l\u00e0 n\u01a1i di\u1ec5n ra nhi\u1ec1u ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u0103n h\u00f3a mang \u0111\u1eadm b\u1ea3n s\u1eafc d\u00e2n t\u1ed9c. Qua nh\u1eefng b\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh ch\u1ee5p l\u1ec5 h\u1ed9i, m\u00faa r\u1ed1i n\u01b0\u1edbc hay h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh c\u00e1c ngh\u1ec7 nh\u00e2n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u1ed1 bi\u1ec3u di\u1ec5n, ph\u1ed1 c\u1ed5 hi\u1ec7n l\u00ean nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t s\u00e2n kh\u1ea5u l\u1edbn, n\u01a1i ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ed3n Vi\u1ec7t qua t\u1eebng \u0111i\u1ec7u m\u00faa, ti\u1ebfng \u0111\u00e0n v\u00e0 l\u1eddi ca. Nh\u1eefng b\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh n\u00e0y mang \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t g\u00f3c nh\u00ecn v\u0103n h\u00f3a s\u00e2u s\u1eafc, gi\u00fap ng\u01b0\u1eddi xem th\u1ea5u hi\u1ec3u th\u00eam v\u1ec1 truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng v\u00e0 v\u0103n h\u00f3a c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i n\u00f3i ri\u00eang v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u00f3i chung.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_8300\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8300\" style=\"width: 768px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-8300 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/hanoireview.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/hinh-anh-ve-pho-co-ha-noi-1731381203.jpg\" alt=\"h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u0111\u1eb9p t\u1ea1i ph\u1ed1 c\u1ed5 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i\" width=\"768\" height=\"1152\" srcset=\"https:\/\/hanoireview.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/hinh-anh-ve-pho-co-ha-noi-1731381203.jpg 768w, https:\/\/hanoireview.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/hinh-anh-ve-pho-co-ha-noi-1731381203-227x340.jpg 227w, https:\/\/hanoireview.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/hinh-anh-ve-pho-co-ha-noi-1731381203-512x768.jpg 512w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-8300\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">M\u1ed7i n\u0103m hoa \u0111\u00e0o n\u1edf &#8211; L\u1ea1i th\u1ea5y \u00f4ng \u0110\u1ed3 gi\u00e0 &#8211; B\u00e0y m\u1ef1c t\u00e0u gi\u1ea5y \u0111\u1ecf &#8211; Tr\u00ean ph\u1ed1 \u0110\u00f4ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi qua.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<figure id=\"attachment_8302\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8302\" style=\"width: 768px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-8302 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/hanoireview.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/hinh-anh-ve-pho-co-ha-noi-1731381414.jpg\" alt=\"h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u0111\u1eb9p v\u1ec1 ph\u1ed1 c\u1ed5\" width=\"768\" height=\"512\" srcset=\"https:\/\/hanoireview.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/hinh-anh-ve-pho-co-ha-noi-1731381414.jpg 768w, https:\/\/hanoireview.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/hinh-anh-ve-pho-co-ha-noi-1731381414-455x303.jpg 455w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-8302\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ngh\u1ec7 thu\u1eadt th\u01b0 ph\u00e1p, n\u00e9t \u0111\u1eb9p v\u0103n ho\u00e1 ng\u00e0n \u0111\u1eddi v\u1eabn c\u00f2n l\u01b0u gi\u1eef<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<figure id=\"attachment_8332\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8332\" style=\"width: 768px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-8332 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/hanoireview.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/hinh-anh-ve-pho-co-ha-noi-1731384564.jpg\" alt=\"h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh v\u1ec1 ph\u1ed1 c\u1ed5 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i\" width=\"768\" height=\"503\" srcset=\"https:\/\/hanoireview.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/hinh-anh-ve-pho-co-ha-noi-1731384564.jpg 768w, https:\/\/hanoireview.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/hinh-anh-ve-pho-co-ha-noi-1731384564-455x298.jpg 455w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-8332\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Bi\u1ec3u di\u1ec5n m\u00faa r\u1ed1i n\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1ea1i Ph\u1ed1 C\u1ed5 mang \u0111\u1eadm truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng v\u0103n ho\u00e1<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p class=\"p3\"><b>5. Ng\u1eafm Ph\u1ed1 C\u1ed5 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i qua B\u1ed9 S\u01b0u T\u1eadp nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u1ea5t<\/b><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\">\u0110\u1ec3 kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 th\u00eam v\u1ebb \u0111\u1eb9p c\u1ee7a ph\u1ed1 c\u1ed5 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u00ecm \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng b\u1ed9 s\u01b0u t\u1eadp \u1ea3nh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1eeb c\u00e1c ngu\u1ed3n uy t\u00edn.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_8286\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8286\" style=\"width: 768px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-8286 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/hanoireview.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/hinh-anh-ve-pho-co-ha-noi-1731378946.jpg\" alt=\"h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u0111\u1eb9p v\u1ec1 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i\" width=\"768\" height=\"512\" srcset=\"https:\/\/hanoireview.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/hinh-anh-ve-pho-co-ha-noi-1731378946.jpg 768w, https:\/\/hanoireview.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/hinh-anh-ve-pho-co-ha-noi-1731378946-455x303.jpg 455w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-8286\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">C\u1ed9t c\u1edd H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i &#8211; bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng thi\u00eang li\u00eang v\u00e0 h\u00e0o h\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a Th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<figure id=\"attachment_8287\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8287\" style=\"width: 768px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-8287 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/hanoireview.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/hinh-anh-ve-pho-co-ha-noi-1731379013.jpg\" alt=\"h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u0111\u1eb9p v\u1ec1 ph\u1ed1 c\u1ed5 h\u00e0 n\u1ed9i\" width=\"768\" height=\"512\" srcset=\"https:\/\/hanoireview.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/hinh-anh-ve-pho-co-ha-noi-1731379013.jpg 768w, https:\/\/hanoireview.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/hinh-anh-ve-pho-co-ha-noi-1731379013-455x303.jpg 455w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-8287\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">M\u1ed9t g\u00e1nh hoa m\u00f9a thu H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i tr\u00ean ph\u1ed1 c\u1ed5<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<figure id=\"attachment_8290\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8290\" style=\"width: 768px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-8290 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/hanoireview.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/hinh-anh-ve-pho-co-ha-noi-1731379313.jpg\" alt=\"h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u0111\u1eb9p v\u1ec1 ph\u1ed1 c\u1ed5 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i\" width=\"768\" height=\"1152\" srcset=\"https:\/\/hanoireview.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/hinh-anh-ve-pho-co-ha-noi-1731379313.jpg 768w, https:\/\/hanoireview.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/hinh-anh-ve-pho-co-ha-noi-1731379313-227x340.jpg 227w, https:\/\/hanoireview.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/hinh-anh-ve-pho-co-ha-noi-1731379313-512x768.jpg 512w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-8290\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">M\u1ed9t c\u1eeda hi\u1ec7u t\u1ea1i Ph\u1ed1 c\u1ed5 mang \u0111\u1eadm n\u00e9t ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac c\u1ed5 x\u01b0a c\u00f2n l\u01b0u gi\u1eef<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<figure id=\"attachment_8292\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8292\" style=\"width: 768px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-8292 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/hanoireview.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/hinh-anh-ve-pho-co-ha-noi-1731379423.jpg\" alt=\"h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u0111\u1eb9p v\u1ec1 ph\u1ed1 c\u1ed5 h\u00e0 n\u1ed9i\" width=\"768\" height=\"1367\" srcset=\"https:\/\/hanoireview.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/hinh-anh-ve-pho-co-ha-noi-1731379423.jpg 768w, https:\/\/hanoireview.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/hinh-anh-ve-pho-co-ha-noi-1731379423-191x340.jpg 191w, https:\/\/hanoireview.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/hinh-anh-ve-pho-co-ha-noi-1731379423-431x768.jpg 431w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-8292\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">C\u00e0 ph\u00ea b\u1ec7t \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1eaft &#8211; tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng khi \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi ph\u1ed1 C\u1ed5<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<figure id=\"attachment_8349\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8349\" style=\"width: 768px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-8349 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/hanoireview.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/hinh-anh-ve-pho-co-ha-noi-1731386314.jpg\" alt=\"h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u0111\u1eb9p v\u1ec1 ph\u1ed1 c\u1ed5 h\u00e0 n\u1ed9i\" width=\"768\" height=\"512\" srcset=\"https:\/\/hanoireview.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/hinh-anh-ve-pho-co-ha-noi-1731386314.jpg 768w, https:\/\/hanoireview.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/hinh-anh-ve-pho-co-ha-noi-1731386314-455x303.jpg 455w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-8349\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Du kh\u00e1ch tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m ph\u1ed1 t\u00e0u H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i v\u00e0 th\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed3 u\u1ed1ng t\u1ea1i qu\u00e1n c\u00e0 ph\u00ea b\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1eaft<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<figure id=\"attachment_8293\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8293\" style=\"width: 768px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-8293 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/hanoireview.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/hinh-anh-ve-pho-co-ha-noi-1731379578.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1152\" srcset=\"https:\/\/hanoireview.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/hinh-anh-ve-pho-co-ha-noi-1731379578.jpg 768w, https:\/\/hanoireview.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/hinh-anh-ve-pho-co-ha-noi-1731379578-227x340.jpg 227w, https:\/\/hanoireview.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/hinh-anh-ve-pho-co-ha-noi-1731379578-512x768.jpg 512w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-8293\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">M\u1ed9t con ng\u00f5 nh\u1ecf y\u00ean b\u00ecnh gi\u1eefa l\u00f2ng ph\u1ed1 c\u1ed5<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<figure id=\"attachment_8307\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8307\" style=\"width: 768px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-8307 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/hanoireview.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/hinh-anh-ve-pho-co-ha-noi-1731382126.jpg\" alt=\"h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh v\u1ec1 ph\u1ed1 c\u1ed5 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i\" width=\"768\" height=\"511\" srcset=\"https:\/\/hanoireview.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/hinh-anh-ve-pho-co-ha-noi-1731382126.jpg 768w, https:\/\/hanoireview.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/hinh-anh-ve-pho-co-ha-noi-1731382126-455x303.jpg 455w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-8307\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">M\u1ed9t h\u00e0ng qu\u00e1n v\u1ec9a h\u00e8 v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng m\u00f3n \u0103n truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1eadm \u0111\u00e0<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<figure id=\"attachment_8310\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8310\" style=\"width: 768px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-8310 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/hanoireview.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/hinh-anh-ve-pho-co-ha-noi-1731382685.jpg\" alt=\"h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh v\u1ec1 ph\u1ed1 c\u1ed5\" width=\"768\" height=\"515\" srcset=\"https:\/\/hanoireview.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/hinh-anh-ve-pho-co-ha-noi-1731382685.jpg 768w, https:\/\/hanoireview.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/hinh-anh-ve-pho-co-ha-noi-1731382685-455x305.jpg 455w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-8310\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">M\u1ed9t g\u00f3c ph\u1ed1 c\u1ed5 t\u1ea5p n\u1eadp v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u1eeda hi\u1ec7u san s\u00e1t nhau<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<figure id=\"attachment_8316\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8316\" style=\"width: 768px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-8316 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/hanoireview.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/hinh-anh-ve-pho-co-ha-noi-1731383035.jpg\" alt=\"h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh v\u1ec1 ph\u1ed1 c\u1ed5 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i\" width=\"768\" height=\"491\" srcset=\"https:\/\/hanoireview.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/hinh-anh-ve-pho-co-ha-noi-1731383035.jpg 768w, https:\/\/hanoireview.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/hinh-anh-ve-pho-co-ha-noi-1731383035-455x291.jpg 455w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-8316\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">M\u1ed9t g\u00f3c ph\u1ed1 c\u1ed5 v\u1eabn gi\u1eef nguy\u00ean v\u1eb9n ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac t\u1eeb th\u1ebf k\u1ef7 20<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<figure id=\"attachment_8330\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8330\" style=\"width: 768px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-8330 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/hanoireview.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/hinh-anh-ve-pho-co-ha-noi-1731384433.jpg\" alt=\"h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh v\u1ec1 ph\u1ed1 c\u1ed5 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i\" width=\"768\" height=\"493\" srcset=\"https:\/\/hanoireview.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/hinh-anh-ve-pho-co-ha-noi-1731384433.jpg 768w, https:\/\/hanoireview.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/hinh-anh-ve-pho-co-ha-noi-1731384433-455x292.jpg 455w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-8330\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ph\u1ed1 bia T\u1ea1 Hi\u1ec7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1edd s\u00f4i \u0111\u1ed9ng<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<figure id=\"attachment_8335\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8335\" style=\"width: 768px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-8335 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/hanoireview.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/hinh-anh-ve-pho-co-ha-noi-1731384653.jpg\" alt=\"ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh t\u1ea1i ph\u1ed1 c\u1ed5\" width=\"768\" height=\"512\" srcset=\"https:\/\/hanoireview.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/hinh-anh-ve-pho-co-ha-noi-1731384653.jpg 768w, https:\/\/hanoireview.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/hinh-anh-ve-pho-co-ha-noi-1731384653-455x303.jpg 455w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-8335\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh t\u1ea1i ph\u1ed1 c\u1ed5 l\u01b0u gi\u1eef nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u0111\u1eb9p \u0111\u1ebd<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<figure id=\"attachment_8339\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8339\" style=\"width: 768px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-8339 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/hanoireview.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/hinh-anh-ve-pho-co-ha-noi-1731384833.jpg\" alt=\"h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u0111\u1eb9p v\u1ec1 ph\u1ed1 c\u1ed5 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i\" width=\"768\" height=\"556\" srcset=\"https:\/\/hanoireview.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/hinh-anh-ve-pho-co-ha-noi-1731384833.jpg 768w, https:\/\/hanoireview.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/hinh-anh-ve-pho-co-ha-noi-1731384833-455x329.jpg 455w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-8339\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">M\u1ed9t g\u00f3c t\u1ea1p ho\u00e1 t\u1ea1i ph\u1ed1 B\u00e1t \u0110\u00e0n g\u1ee3i m\u1ed9t ni\u1ec1m ho\u00e0i c\u1ed5<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<figure id=\"attachment_8341\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8341\" style=\"width: 768px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-8341 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/hanoireview.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/hinh-anh-ve-pho-co-ha-noi-1731384949.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"512\" srcset=\"https:\/\/hanoireview.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/hinh-anh-ve-pho-co-ha-noi-1731384949.jpg 768w, https:\/\/hanoireview.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/hinh-anh-ve-pho-co-ha-noi-1731384949-455x303.jpg 455w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-8341\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">M\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i bi\u1ec3u di\u1ec5n m\u00faa l\u00e2n t\u1ea1i ph\u1ed1 T\u1ea1 Hi\u1ec7n mang \u0111\u1eadm n\u00e9t v\u0103n ho\u00e1 truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<figure id=\"attachment_8346\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8346\" style=\"width: 768px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-8346 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/hanoireview.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/hinh-anh-ve-pho-co-ha-noi-1731385222.jpg\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u0111\u1eb9p v\u1ec1 Ph\u1ed1 c\u1ed5 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i\" width=\"768\" height=\"511\" srcset=\"https:\/\/hanoireview.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/hinh-anh-ve-pho-co-ha-noi-1731385222.jpg 768w, https:\/\/hanoireview.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/hinh-anh-ve-pho-co-ha-noi-1731385222-455x303.jpg 455w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-8346\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">L\u1ec5 h\u1ed9i T\u1ebft Trung Thu t\u1ea1i Ph\u1ed1 c\u1ed5 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p class=\"p4\">Ph\u1ed1 c\u1ed5 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t di s\u1ea3n v\u0103n h\u00f3a \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, n\u01a1i m\u00e0 m\u1ed7i con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng, m\u1ed7i ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec1u k\u1ec3 m\u1ed9t c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n l\u1ecbch s\u1eed, v\u00e0 b\u1ed9 s\u01b0u t\u1eadp h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u0111\u1eb9p v\u1ec1 ph\u1ed1 c\u1ed5 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 v\u1ebb \u0111\u1eb9p c\u1ee7a n\u01a1i n\u00e0y. Qua nh\u1eefng b\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh \u0111\u1ea7y c\u1ea3m x\u00fac, ng\u01b0\u1eddi xem kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u1eafm nh\u00ecn v\u1ebb \u0111\u1eb9p c\u1ee7a ph\u1ed1 c\u1ed5 m\u00e0 c\u00f2n c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn nh\u1ecbp s\u1ed1ng, v\u0103n h\u00f3a v\u00e0 linh h\u1ed3n c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i x\u01b0a c\u0169 v\u1eabn s\u1ed1ng m\u00e3i c\u00f9ng th\u1eddi gian.<\/p>\n<div id=\"sticky-after-content\" class=\"sticky-after-content\">\n<p class=\"sticky-heading\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n quan t\u00e2m<\/p>\n<ul class=\"list-sticky-post\">\n<li class=\"post\"><a href=\"https:\/\/hanoireview.vn\/pho-co-ha-noi-7828.html\">Ph\u1ed1 C\u1ed5 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i<\/a>: N\u01a1i l\u01b0u gi\u1eef h\u1ed3n x\u01b0a trong t\u1eebng con ng\u00f5 nh\u1ecf<\/li>\n<li>10 <a href=\"https:\/\/hanoireview.vn\/topAZ\/quan-com-ngon-tai-pho-co-ha-noi\">Qu\u00e1n c\u01a1m ngon t\u1ea1i Ph\u1ed1 C\u1ed5 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i<\/a> \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng v\u1ecb truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng<\/li>\n<li>15 <a href=\"https:\/\/hanoireview.vn\/topAZ\/quan-cafe-pho-co\">Qu\u00e1n Cafe Ph\u1ed1 C\u1ed5<\/a> nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh ph\u1ea3i th\u1eed khi \u0111\u1ebfn H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i<\/li>\n<li>10 <a href=\"https:\/\/hanoireview.vn\/topAZ\/quan-bun-dau-mam-tom-pho-co-ha-noi\">Qu\u00e1n b\u00fan \u0111\u1eadu m\u1eafm t\u00f4m Ph\u1ed1 C\u1ed5 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i<\/a> ngon n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng, l\u00e2u \u0111\u1eddi<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Ph\u1ed1 c\u1ed5 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t kh\u00f4ng gian \u0111\u1eadm ch\u1ea5t v\u0103n h\u00f3a v\u00e0 l\u1ecbch s\u1eed m\u00e0 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 n\u01a1i h\u1ed9i t\u1ee5 nh\u1eefng n\u00e9t \u0111\u1eb9p \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ea5t kinh k\u1ef3 x\u01b0a. Qua t\u1eebng g\u00f3c ph\u1ed1, t\u1eebng con ng\u00f5 nh\u1ecf h\u1eb9p, t\u1eebng ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 c\u1ed5 k\u00ednh, ph\u1ed1 c\u1ed5 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i ph\u00e1c h\u1ecda l\u00ean m\u1ed9t [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":20,"featured_media":8341,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[1],"tags":[],"locations":[11],"class_list":["post-8281","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail"